  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Perfect timing. #p313# of #m10002000# has requested a special item for village maintenance. I don’t think I can finish it on my own in time. …Would you help me?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Much appreciated. I need to craft #t1082000#, but I’m short on #b#t4003007##k. Could you craft some for me? You probably thought #t1082000# don't suit fairies very well, didn’t you? Hmph. Still, fairy hands are far more delicate than you think. And while you’re at it, deal with some of the #r#o13#s#k around the village. They keep getting in the way whenever I go out to gather materials. I’ll be waiting."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "An apprentice refusing a master’s request… Is that how things work in the human world?"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Good. This is exactly what I needed. As expected—you really are my first human apprentice. Heh…"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Here. Take this #t2002009# as your reward. It should make training your tailoring skills a bit easier."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "But this is troublesome… I have a feeling #p313# will keep making requests like this. It seems I might be relying on your help more often. I’ll call on you again next time."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
